item.content:encoded:
I am a Management Information Systems Major with a focused minor in Cybersecurity at Texas A&M University in College Station, TX. Originally from Deer Park, TX, I am now working to complete my undergraduate degree with an expected graduation date of December 2024.

Currently, I am working to further my technical skills through the completion of various projects and studies for certification in CompTIA’s Security+ and Network+. Feel free to check out my projects page to learn more! In the meantime, here is a list of tools I have found myself working with recently:

  • Linux
  • HTML/CSS
  • Amazon Web Services
  • Microsoft Office
  • Wireshark
